50|$|The regular weekly Torah portion is {{not read}} on these <b>Sabbaths</b> and instead there are special Torah {{readings}} {{based on the}} uniqueness of each holiday and the Three Pilgrim Festivals. There are also special maftirs ("additional Torah readings") and Haftarahs (readings from the prophets.) See Haftarot for special <b>Sabbaths,</b> Festivals, and Fast Days.|$|R
